---

<BaseLayout
  title="Roof Warranties | 15-Year Workmanship Guarantee | Happy Roof"
  description="Happy Roof offers an up to Up to 15-year workmanship warranty on shingle, metal & tile roofs, plus 10 years on flat roofs. In writing, every time. Tampa Bay, FL."
  canonical="https://happyroof.com/warranties"
  ogTitle="Roofing Warranties | Happy Roof Tampa Bay"
  ogDescription="Up to 15-year workmanship warranty on shingle, metal & tile roofs. 10 years on flat roofs. In writing, every time. Tampa Bay, FL."
  schema={schema}
>

<style is:inline>
.check-dot{width:20px;height:20px;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;background:rgba(230,168,23,.1);flex-shrink:0;margin-top:.15rem}
    .x-dot{width:20px;height:20px;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;background:rgba(59,159,217,.1);flex-shrink:0;margin-top:.15rem}
    /* Hero photo bg */
</style>

<section class="relative overflow-hidden" style="padding:8rem 0 5rem;background:#FFFFFF">
  <div class="hero-photo-bg" style="background-image:url('/Brand%20Assets/Photos/architectural-shingle-roof-tampa-bay.jpg')"></div>
  <div class="hero-photo-overlay"></div>
  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-5xl mx-auto px-5 text-center">
    <p class="sl mb-4" style="color:#888888">Our Guarantee</p>
    <h1 class="font-display font-black tracking-tightest mb-5" style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(3rem,7vw,5.5rem);line-height:.88;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:#1A1A1A">
      REAL WARRANTIES.<br/><span style="color:#E6A817">IN WRITING.</span>
    </h1>
    <p style="color:#555555;font-size:1.1rem;line-height:1.75;max-width:560px;margin:0 auto 2.5rem">
      Most roofers in Tampa Bay offer 1–5 years of workmanship coverage. We offer 15. In writing, on every job, because we stand behind our work.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 justify-center">
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-p" style="font-size:1.1rem;padding:.9rem 2rem">Get a Free Estimate</a>
      <a href="tel:8135957663" class="btn-o call-tracking-number" style="font-size:1rem;padding:.85rem 1.8rem">Call (813) 595-7663</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══════ COMPARISON TABLE ══════ -->
<section style="background:#F7F7F7;padding:4rem 0 5rem">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-5">
    <div class="text-center mb-10">
      <p class="sl mb-3" style="color:#3B9FD9">Side by Side</p>
      <h2 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);line-height:.92;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:#1A1A1A;text-transform:uppercase">
        HAPPY ROOF VS. INDUSTRY AVERAGE
      </h2>
    </div>
    <div class="overflow-x-auto">
      <table style="width:100%;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:0;border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #E0E0E0">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th style="padding:1.2rem 1.5rem;text-align:left;font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:.85rem;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#888888;background:#F7F7F7;border-bottom:1px solid #E0E0E0">Roof Type</th>
            <th style="padding:1.2rem 1.5rem;text-align:center;font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:.95rem;letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#FFFFFF;background:#1A1A1A;border-bottom:1px solid #E0E0E0">
              <span style="color:#E6A817">Happy Roof</span>
            </th>
            <th style="padding:1.2rem 1.5rem;text-align:center;font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:.85rem;letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#888888;background:#F7F7F7;border-bottom:1px solid #E0E0E0">Industry Average</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding:1rem 1.5rem;font-weight:600;font-size:.95rem;border-bottom:1px solid #E0E0E0">Asphalt Shingles</td>
            <td style="padding:1rem 1.5rem;text-align:center;font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.3rem;color:#E6A817;border-bottom:1px solid #E0E0E0;background:rgba(230,168,23,.04)">15 YEARS</td>
            <td style="padding:1rem 1.5rem;text-align:center;font-size:.9rem;color:#888888;border-bottom:1px solid #E0E0E0">1–5 Years</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding:1rem 1.5rem;font-weight:600;font-size:.95rem;border-bottom:1px solid #E0E0E0">Metal Roofing</td>
            <td style="padding:1rem 1.5rem;text-align:center;font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.3rem;color:#E6A817;border-bottom:1px solid #E0E0E0;background:rgba(230,168,23,.04)">15 YEARS</td>
            <td style="padding:1rem 1.5rem;text-align:center;font-size:.9rem;color:#888888;border-bottom:1px solid #E0E0E0">1–5 Years</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding:1rem 1.5rem;font-weight:600;font-size:.95rem;border-bottom:1px solid #E0E0E0">Tile Roofing</td>
            <td style="padding:1rem 1.5rem;text-align:center;font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.3rem;color:#E6A817;border-bottom:1px solid #E0E0E0;background:rgba(230,168,23,.04)">15 YEARS</td>
            <td style="padding:1rem 1.5rem;text-align:center;font-size:.9rem;color:#888888;border-bottom:1px solid #E0E0E0">1–5 Years</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding:1rem 1.5rem;font-weight:600;font-size:.95rem">Flat Roof (TPO/EPDM)</td>
            <td style="padding:1rem 1.5rem;text-align:center;font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.3rem;color:#E6A817;background:rgba(230,168,23,.04)">10 YEARS</td>
            <td style="padding:1rem 1.5rem;text-align:center;font-size:.9rem;color:#888888">1–2 Years</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
    <p style="color:#888888;font-size:.78rem;text-align:center;margin-top:1rem">All Happy Roof workmanship warranties are provided in writing at project completion.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══════ WHAT'S COVERED / WHAT'S NOT ══════ -->
<section style="background:#FFFFFF;padding:4rem 0 5rem">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-5">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <p class="sl mb-3" style="color:#3B9FD9">The Details</p>
      <h2 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);line-height:.92;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:#1A1A1A;text-transform:uppercase">
        WHAT'S COVERED &amp; WHAT'S NOT
      </h2>
    </div>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <!-- Covered -->
      <div style="background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #E0E0E0;border-radius:20px;padding:2rem">
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.6rem;margin-bottom:1.5rem">
          <div style="width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:10px;background:rgba(230,168,23,.1);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1.2rem;letter-spacing:.06em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#1A1A1A">What's Covered</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="check"><div class="check-dot"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg></div><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.7">Leaks caused by installation defects or workmanship errors</p></div>
        <div class="check"><div class="check-dot"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg></div><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.7">Improperly installed flashing, underlayment, or drip edge</p></div>
        <div class="check"><div class="check-dot"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg></div><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.7">Nail pops or fastener failures from our installation</p></div>
        <div class="check"><div class="check-dot"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg></div><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.7">Vent boot, pipe collar, or penetration seal failures</p></div>
        <div class="check"><div class="check-dot"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg></div><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.7">Ridge cap or hip cap installation defects</p></div>
        <div class="check"><div class="check-dot"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg></div><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.7">Valley, step flashing, and counter flashing issues</p></div>
      </div>
      <!-- Not Covered -->
      <div style="background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #E0E0E0;border-radius:20px;padding:2rem">
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.6rem;margin-bottom:1.5rem">
          <div style="width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:10px;background:rgba(59,159,217,.1);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#3B9FD9" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M18 6L6 18"/><path d="M6 6l12 12"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1.2rem;letter-spacing:.06em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#1A1A1A">What's Not Covered</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="check"><div class="x-dot"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#3B9FD9" stroke-width="3"><path d="M18 6L6 18"/><path d="M6 6l12 12"/></svg></div><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.7">Damage caused by hurricanes, storms, or falling debris</p></div>
        <div class="check"><div class="x-dot"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#3B9FD9" stroke-width="3"><path d="M18 6L6 18"/><path d="M6 6l12 12"/></svg></div><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.7">Modifications or repairs made by others after installation</p></div>
        <div class="check"><div class="x-dot"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#3B9FD9" stroke-width="3"><path d="M18 6L6 18"/><path d="M6 6l12 12"/></svg></div><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.7">Damage from lack of maintenance or neglect</p></div>
        <div class="check"><div class="x-dot"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#3B9FD9" stroke-width="3"><path d="M18 6L6 18"/><path d="M6 6l12 12"/></svg></div><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.7">Normal wear and tear over time</p></div>
        <div class="check"><div class="x-dot"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#3B9FD9" stroke-width="3"><path d="M18 6L6 18"/><path d="M6 6l12 12"/></svg></div><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.7">Structural movement or settling of the building</p></div>
        <div class="check"><div class="x-dot"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#3B9FD9" stroke-width="3"><path d="M18 6L6 18"/><path d="M6 6l12 12"/></svg></div><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.7">Material defects (covered separately by manufacturer warranty)</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══════ HOW TO FILE A CLAIM ══════ -->
<section style="background:#F7F7F7;padding:4rem 0 5rem">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-5">
    <div class="text-center mb-10">
      <p class="sl mb-3" style="color:#3B9FD9">Simple Process</p>
      <h2 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);line-height:.92;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:#1A1A1A;text-transform:uppercase">
        HOW TO FILE A WARRANTY CLAIM
      </h2>
    </div>
    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <div style="background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #E0E0E0;border-radius:18px;padding:2rem;text-align:center">
        <div style="width:56px;height:56px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(230,168,23,.1);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin:0 auto 1.2rem">
          <span style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:900;font-size:1.4rem;color:#E6A817">1</span>
        </div>
        <h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1rem;letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.5rem">CALL US</h3>
        <p style="color:#555555;font-size:.88rem;line-height:1.7">Call <a href="tel:8135957663" class="call-tracking-number" style="color:#3B9FD9;text-decoration:underline">(813) 595-7663</a> or email info@happyroof.com to report the issue. Describe the problem and when you first noticed it.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #E0E0E0;border-radius:18px;padding:2rem;text-align:center">
        <div style="width:56px;height:56px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(230,168,23,.1);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin:0 auto 1.2rem">
          <span style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:900;font-size:1.4rem;color:#E6A817">2</span>
        </div>
        <h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1rem;letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.5rem">WE INSPECT</h3>
        <p style="color:#555555;font-size:.88rem;line-height:1.7">We'll schedule an on-site inspection within 48 hours to assess the issue, identify the cause, and determine if it's covered under your warranty.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #E0E0E0;border-radius:18px;padding:2rem;text-align:center">
        <div style="width:56px;height:56px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(230,168,23,.1);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin:0 auto 1.2rem">
          <span style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:900;font-size:1.4rem;color:#E6A817">3</span>
        </div>
        <h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1rem;letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.5rem">WE FIX IT</h3>
        <p style="color:#555555;font-size:.88rem;line-height:1.7">If the issue is covered under your workmanship warranty, we'll repair it at no cost to you. No runaround, no excuses - just the fix.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══════ MANUFACTURER WARRANTIES ══════ -->
<section style="background:#FFFFFF;padding:4rem 0 5rem">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-5">
    <div class="text-center mb-10">
      <p class="sl mb-3" style="color:#3B9FD9">Material Protection</p>
      <h2 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);line-height:.92;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:#1A1A1A;text-transform:uppercase">
        MANUFACTURER WARRANTIES
      </h2>
      <p style="color:#555555;font-size:1rem;line-height:1.75;max-width:600px;margin:.75rem auto 0">In addition to our workmanship warranty, your roof is protected by manufacturer material warranties from the industry's top brands.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="max-width:560px;margin:0 auto">
      <!-- Owens Corning - Single Card -->
      <div style="background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #E0E0E0;border-radius:20px;padding:2rem;transition:border-color .25s" onmouseover="this.style.borderColor='rgba(230,168,23,.3)'" onmouseout="this.style.borderColor='#E0E0E0'">
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.8rem;margin-bottom:1.2rem">
          <div style="width:48px;height:48px;border-radius:12px;background:rgba(230,168,23,.1);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1.2rem;letter-spacing:.06em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#1A1A1A">Owens Corning</h3>
            <p style="color:#888888;font-size:.78rem;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase">Certified Installer</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="check"><div class="check-dot"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg></div><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.7"><strong>Lifetime Limited Warranty</strong> on Duration HDZ, UHDZ, Oakridge, and Berkshire shingles</p></div>
        <div class="check"><div class="check-dot"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg></div><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.7"><strong>SureNail Technology:</strong> superior wind resistance rated up to 130 mph</p></div>
        <div class="check"><div class="check-dot"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg></div><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.7">Covers manufacturing defects and premature material failure</p></div>
        <div class="check"><div class="check-dot"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg></div><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.7">Owens Corning offers Preferred Protection and Platinum Protection enhanced warranty programs</p></div>
        <div style="margin-top:1rem;text-align:center"><a href="https://www.owenscorning.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:#3B9FD9;font-size:.85rem;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none">owenscorning.com →</a></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══════ WARRANTY STATS BAR ══════ -->
